    <entry>
      <title>hexo</title>
      <link href="/2023/03/13/hexo/"/>
      <url>/2023/03/13/hexo/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="介绍"><a href="#介绍" class="headerlink" title="介绍"></a>介绍</h2><p><code>hexo</code> 渲染成静态文件，可以上传到 <code>GitHub pages</code> <code>cloudflare pages</code> 等免费服务商，不但不怕攻击也不用维护。部署也方便，<del>服务器也不会忘记续费资料全没</del></p><h2 id="使用教程"><a href="#使用教程" class="headerlink" title="使用教程"></a>使用教程</h2><h3 id="写作"><a href="#写作" class="headerlink" title="写作"></a>写作</h3><p><code>hexo new [layout] &lt;title&gt;</code> 创建新博客<br>Hexo 有三种默认布局：<code>post</code>、<code>page</code> 和 <code>draft</code>。在创建这三种不同类型的文件时，它们将会被保存到不同的路径；而您自定义的其他布局和 <code>post</code> 相同，都将储存到 <code>source/_posts</code> 文件夹。</p><p>draft是一种特殊的布局<br><code>hexo publish [layout] &lt;title&gt;</code> 可以将它移动到 <code>source</code></p><h4 id="自定义-模板-scaffold"><a href="#自定义-模板-scaffold" class="headerlink" title="自定义 模板 scaffold"></a>自定义 模板 <em>scaffold</em></h4><p>hexo 会尝试在 <code>scaffold</code>  找模板文件</p><h4 id="tags-amp-categories"><a href="#tags-amp-categories" class="headerlink" title="tags &amp; categories"></a>tags &amp; categories</h4><p>需要注意的是 在hexo中 分类和tag 不同，分类是有层级的<br>详情见 <em><a href="https://hexo.io/zh-cn/docs/front-matter#%E5%88%86%E7%B1%BB%E5%92%8C%E6%A0%87%E7%AD%BE">Front-matter -分类和标签| Hexo</a></em></p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">tags:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="string">Games</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="string">PS5</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">categories:</span>  </span><br><span class="line">  <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="string">Diary</span>  </span><br><span class="line">  <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="string">Life</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">categories:</span>  </span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">-</span> [<span class="string">Diary</span>, <span class="string">PlayStation</span>]  </span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">-</span> [<span class="string">Diary</span>, <span class="string">Games</span>]  </span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">-</span> [<span class="string">Life</span>]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="相对引用图片"><a href="#相对引用图片" class="headerlink" title="相对引用图片"></a>相对引用图片</h4><p>开启 <code>post_asset_folder</code> 详情见 配置文件 <code>Writing</code> 部分<br>使用 <code>![](&lt;filename&gt;)</code> 引用图片即可，文件放在 与 md 同名在同一目录下文件夹内</p><h2 id="部署过程"><a href="#部署过程" class="headerlink" title="部署过程"></a>部署过程</h2><figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install <span class="literal">-g</span> hexo<span class="literal">-cli</span> </span><br><span class="line">hexo init &lt;name&gt;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> &lt;name&gt;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 主题</span></span><br><span class="line">git clone https://github.com/probberechts/hexo<span class="literal">-theme-cactus</span>.git themes/cactu</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># serach</span></span><br><span class="line">npm install hexo<span class="literal">-generator-search</span> <span class="literal">--save</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 创建页面</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo new page about</span><br><span class="line">hexo new page tags</span><br><span class="line">hexo new page search</span><br><span class="line">hexo new page categories</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#Writing</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">post_asset_folder:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">marked:</span> <span class="comment"># 使用 Markdown 嵌入图片 无需使用 asset_img</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">prependRoot:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">postAsset:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># cacatus</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">theme_config:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">nav:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">home:</span> <span class="string">/</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">about:</span> <span class="string">/about/</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">tag:</span> <span class="string">/tags/</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">category:</span> <span class="string">/categories/</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">search:</span> <span class="string">/search/</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">articles:</span> <span class="string">/archives/</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">projects:</span> <span class="string">https://github.com/catnaut</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">### LINK_NAME: URL</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">posts_overview:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">show_all_posts:</span> <span class="literal">false</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">post_count:</span> <span class="number">5</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">social_links:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">github:</span> <span class="string">https://github.com/catnaut</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">telegram:</span> <span class="string">your-telegram-url</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">deploy:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">type:</span> <span class="string">git·</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">repo:</span> <span class="string">git@github_catnaut:catnaut/catnaut.github.io.git</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">branch:</span> <span class="string">main</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="踩坑"><a href="#踩坑" class="headerlink" title="踩坑"></a>踩坑</h3><h4 id="网络问题"><a href="#网络问题" class="headerlink" title="网络问题"></a>网络问题</h4><figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">fatal: unable to access <span class="string">&#x27;https://github.com/catnaut/catnaut.github.io.git/&#x27;</span>: The requested URL returned error: <span class="number">403</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>使用 http协议 时 挂了代理，设了 <code>$http_proxy</code> 也始终无效，最后使用 ssh 协议解决</p><h4 id="ssh-身份认证"><a href="#ssh-身份认证" class="headerlink" title="ssh 身份认证"></a>ssh 身份认证</h4><p>这个身份认证问题可能和 <code>powershell</code> 和 <code>ssh-agent</code> 有关<br>背景：我有多个 <code>sshkey</code> </p><figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="variable">$</span> ssh git@github.com</span><br><span class="line">git@github.com: Permission denied (publickey).</span><br><span class="line"><span class="variable">$</span> ssh<span class="literal">-agent</span>.exe</span><br><span class="line"><span class="variable">$</span> ssh git@github.com</span><br><span class="line">PTY allocation request failed on channel <span class="number">0</span></span><br><span class="line">Hi catnaut! You<span class="string">&#x27;ve successfully authenticated, but GitHub does not provide shell access.</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">Connection to github.com closed.</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>但是<code>hexo d</code> 死活部署不成功，最后写了个 ssh配置才解决的</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># ~/.ssh/config</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"># github_catnaut</span><br><span class="line">Host github_catnaut</span><br><span class="line">HostName github.com</span><br><span class="line">User git</span><br><span class="line">PreferredAuthentications publickey</span><br><span class="line">IdentityFile &lt;paath_to_ke&gt;</span><br><span class="line">Port 22</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="多用户环境"><a href="#多用户环境" class="headerlink" title="多用户环境"></a>多用户环境</h4><p>在多用户环境下会自动使用git的默认设置，如果要使用本地设置在<code>_config.ymal</code>添加</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">deploy:</span><br><span class="line">  # 其他保留</span><br><span class="line">  name: [git user]</span><br><span class="line">  email: [git email]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>但是 frist commit 还是别的邮箱的 ， 可以通过命令修改后再上传 GitHub</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># 查看 frist commit id</span><br><span class="line">git log </span><br><span class="line">git rebase -i &lt;id&gt;</span><br><span class="line">git commit --amend --author=&quot;Author Name &lt;email@address.com&gt;&quot;</span><br><span class="line"># 最后切换回去</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="感想"><a href="#感想" class="headerlink" title="感想"></a>感想</h2><p><code>catnaut</code> 的中文支持不太好啊，有时间改下字体和样式</p>]]></content>
      
      
