    <entry>
      <title>windows 包管理</title>
      <link href="/2022/12/13/windows-package-management/"/>
      <url>/2022/12/13/windows-package-management/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="前言"><a href="#前言" class="headerlink" title="前言"></a>前言</h2><p>习惯了 <code>pacman</code> 真的回不去了，包管理真香<br>window主流有：<br>    - scoop<br>    - chocolate<br>    - winget</p><h2 id="winget"><a href="#winget" class="headerlink" title="winget"></a>winget</h2><p>微软官方开发的，不过 winget 还没有特别完善<br><a href="https://github.com/microsoft/winget-cli">GitHub - microsoft&#x2F;winget-cli: Windows Package Manager CLI (aka winget)</a><br><a href="https://github.com/microsoft/winget-pkgs">GitHub - microsoft&#x2F;winget-pkgs: The Microsoft community Windows Package Manager manifest repository</a></p><p>安装方法 <a href="https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/windows/package-manager/winget/install">install Command | Microsoft Docs</a><br>win11 预装了，22H以上的 win10 好像也预装了<br><em>一开始居然有一个协议要同意好烦</em></p><h4 id="install"><a href="#install" class="headerlink" title="install"></a>install</h4><p><code>--scope</code> Select install scope (user or machine)</p><h4 id="proxy"><a href="#proxy" class="headerlink" title="proxy"></a>proxy</h4><p>官方没有给与代理支持，只能通过 proxy chains 代理<br>网络问题真他妈服了，垃圾网络环境</p><h3 id="Chocolatey"><a href="#Chocolatey" class="headerlink" title="Chocolatey"></a>Chocolatey</h3><p>choco </p><h3 id="Scoop"><a href="#Scoop" class="headerlink" title="Scoop"></a>Scoop</h3><p>Scoop 勺子 <a href="https://github.com/ScoopInstaller/Scoop">GitHub - ScoopInstaller&#x2F;Scoop: A command-line installer for Windows.</a><br>偏向开发环境的安装，强调无污染，可以脚本集成。我的 Windows初始化脚本 [[Windows_intal_script]] 从这里开始</p><blockquote><p>Scoop installs programs from the command line with a minimal amount of friction. It:<br>Scoop 以最小的冲突安装软件</p><ul><li>Eliminates permission popup windows</li><li>删除权限弹窗</li><li>Hides GUI wizard-style installers</li><li>隐藏 GUI 安装指引 wizard-style: 引导式</li><li>Prevents PATH pollution from installing lots of programs</li><li>放在 path 环境污染</li><li>Avoids unexpected side-effects from installing and uninstalling programs</li><li>防止安装卸载的副作用</li><li>Finds and installs dependencies automatically</li><li>自动寻找依赖</li><li>Performs all the extra setup steps itself to get a working program</li><li>不知道怎么理解</li></ul></blockquote><p><a href="https://github.com/ScoopInstaller/Scoop#multi-connection-downloads-with-aria2">scoop 设置 aria2 多线程下载</a></p><p><a href="https://github.com/ScoopInstaller/Scoop/wiki">Scoop Wiki · GitHub</a></p><h4 id="安装"><a href="#安装" class="headerlink" title="安装"></a>安装</h4><p><a href="https://github.com/ScoopInstaller/Scoop/wiki/Quick-Start">Quick Start · ScoopInstaller&#x2F;Scoop Wiki · GitHub</a></p><h4 id="命令"><a href="#命令" class="headerlink" title="命令"></a>命令</h4><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">scoop install</span><br><span class="line">scoop info </span><br><span class="line">scoop update</span><br><span class="line">scoop search </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="库-bucket"><a href="#库-bucket" class="headerlink" title="库 bucket"></a>库 bucket</h4><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">scoop bucket add java</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="辅助工具"><a href="#辅助工具" class="headerlink" title="辅助工具"></a>辅助工具</h4><p><a href="https://winstall.app/">winstall</a>  可视化搜索网站，一键生成安装命令</p><h2 id="研究过程"><a href="#研究过程" class="headerlink" title="研究过程"></a>研究过程</h2><h3 id="proxy-1"><a href="#proxy-1" class="headerlink" title="proxy"></a>proxy</h3><p>powershell 中 可以通过 <code>$env:http_proxy=&quot;http://127.0.0.1:10809&quot;</code> 设置代理<br>这个效果未知<br><em>reference： <a href="https://qianxu.run/2021/08/18/powershell-proxy/">powershell 设置代理 | qxdn Blog</a></em></p><p>这Windows下代理怎么老是出毛病啊，v2rayN全局也不顶用啊</p><p>无代理情况</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">PS xxx&gt; curl google.com</span><br><span class="line">curl : 无法连接到远程服务器</span><br><span class="line">所在位置 行:1 字符: 1</span><br><span class="line">+ curl google.com</span><br><span class="line">+ ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~</span><br><span class="line">    + CategoryInfo          : InvalidOperation: (System.Net.HttpWebRequest:HttpWebRequest) [Invoke-WebRequest]，WebExce</span><br><span class="line">    ption</span><br><span class="line">    + FullyQualifiedErrorId : WebCmdletWebResponseException,Microsoft.PowerShell.Commands.InvokeWebRequestCommand</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>使用v2rayN 在使用 v2fly 核心时的 http 代理</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">curl -Proxy &quot;http://127.0.0.1:10809&quot; google.com</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">StatusCode        : 200</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>开启全局后</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">curl -Proxy &quot;http://127.0.0.1:10809&quot; google.com</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">StatusCode        : 200</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>在将核心切换回 xray 后问题无法复现，暂时理解为程序bug重启后解决</p><p><strong>此方法对 scoop choco 都无效</strong>，据说 vcpkg 可以使用</p><h4 id="powershell"><a href="#powershell" class="headerlink" title="powershell"></a>powershell</h4><p>powershell 设置代理<br><code> netsh winhttp show proxy</code> 查看代理状态 </p><h4 id="scoop"><a href="#scoop" class="headerlink" title="scoop"></a>scoop</h4><p>无代理下 aria2 下载出现错误<br>scoop关闭 aria2下载 后仍然出现错误</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">PS xxx&gt; scoop install proxychains</span><br><span class="line">WARN  Purging previous failed installation of proxychains.</span><br><span class="line">ERROR &#x27;proxychains&#x27; isn&#x27;t installed correctly.</span><br><span class="line">Removing older version (0.6.8).</span><br><span class="line">&#x27;proxychains&#x27; was uninstalled.</span><br><span class="line">Installing &#x27;proxychains&#x27; (0.6.8) [64bit]</span><br><span class="line">未能解析此远程名称: &#x27;http&#x27;</span><br><span class="line">URL https://github.com/shunf4/proxychains-windows/releases/download/0.6.8/proxychains_0.6.8_win32_x64.zip is not valid</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>网上搜索后发现此问题为 网络问题，可以通过代理解决<br><em>reference： <a href="https://github.com/neolee/pilot/issues/1273">scoop 安装出错，相关疑难里中的方法无法解决 · Issue #1273 · neolee&#x2F;pilot · GitHub</a></em></p><p><code>scoop config proxy &quot;http://127.0.0.1:10809&quot;</code> 在 scoop 内设置 HTTP 代理无效，同样的代理 curl 有效，<del>排除 HTTP代理故障</del> 。查阅文档后发现应该设置为，<code>scoop config proxy &quot;127.0.0.1:10809&quot;</code></p><p><code>scoop config rm proxy</code> 删除代理</p><p>突然间，他就可以正常使用了，我完全不知道什么情况啊，莫名奇妙就开始干活了，我绝望了！</p><p><code>scoop cache</code> 显示已有的软件缓存 <code>scoop cache rm &lt;manifesits&gt;</code> 可以删除指定的缓存 </p><p>aria2 下载应该时会自动传递 proxy 配置 可以正常下载，到此网络问题解决</p><h5 id="python"><a href="#python" class="headerlink" title="python"></a>python</h5><p>安装 Python 3.7 最新版 3.7.13 出现错误</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Downloading python-3.7.13.exe to compute hashes!</span><br><span class="line">远程服务器返回错误: (404) 未找到。</span><br><span class="line">URL https://www.python.org/ftp/python/3.7.13/python-3.7.13.exe#/setup.exe is not valid</span><br><span class="line">Could not install python@3.7.13</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>查看对应下载网页后发现</p><blockquote><p><strong>Note:</strong> The release you are looking at is <strong>Python 3.7.13</strong>, a <strong>security bugfix release</strong> for the legacy <strong>3.7</strong> series which is now in the <strong>security fix</strong> phase of its life cycle. See the <a href="https://www.python.org/downloads/">downloads page</a> for currently supported versions of Python and for the most recent source-only <strong>security fix</strong> release for 3.7. The final <strong>bugfix release</strong> with binary installers for 3.7 was <a href="https://www.python.org/downloads/release/python-379/">3.7.9</a>.<br>3.7.13 还正在 bugfix 阶段，现在有二进制版本的最新的为 3.7.9</p></blockquote><h5 id="java"><a href="#java" class="headerlink" title="java"></a>java</h5><p><code>scoop bucket add java</code></p><h5 id="steam"><a href="#steam" class="headerlink" title="steam"></a>steam</h5><p>不要用 scoop 安装 steam ，没有管理员权限会导致出错，而使用管理员权限，也不符合scoop的理念</p><h5 id="bucket"><a href="#bucket" class="headerlink" title="bucket"></a>bucket</h5><p><a href="https://github.com/rasa/scoop-directory">GitHub - rasa&#x2F;scoop-directory: A searchable directory of buckets for the scoop package manager for Windows</a></p><h3 id="reference"><a href="#reference" class="headerlink" title="reference"></a>reference</h3><p><a href="https://www.thisfaner.com/p/scoop/">Scoop包管理器的相关技巧和知识 – 就是这个范儿</a></p><p><a href="https://sleepyocean.github.io/pages/59439a/#%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85">包管理 - scoop | Captain’s Geek-Island</a></p><p><a href="https://sspai.com/post/52710">给 Scoop 加上这些软件仓库，让它变成强大的 Windows 软件管理器 - 少数派</a> bucket</p>]]></content>
      
      
      
